CONNECTION_TIMEOUT

static final String CONNECTION_TIMEOUT
The connection timeout string. It defines the timeout millisecond for client connection and it can't be out of the timeout millisecond. For example : if the server is not published or shut down and the client can't get data in the timeout period, an exception will be thrown out. The connection timeout value is configured in http.properties.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

RESPONSE_TIMEOUT

static final String RESPONSE_TIMEOUT
The response timeout string. It defines the timeout millisecond for server response and it can't be out of the timeout millisecond. For example : if the server receives the request of the client and can't return data in the timeout period, an exception will be thrown out. The response timeout value is configured in http.properties.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

BUFFER_SIZE

static final String BUFFER_SIZE
The buffer size string. It defines the size of io buffer and the object which is sent from client to server can't be out of the size. The buffer value is configured in http.properties.
